Exploration enrichment pathways with differentially expressed (DE) genes between old versus young

Team Le Grand

02 mai,2022

Pathway explored : REACTOME DEPOSITION OF NEW CENPA CONTAINING NUCLEOSOMES AT THE CENTROMERE

This pathway contain 68 genes.

In these 68 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes DE significant with a major participation in the enrichment (leadingEdge cal by fgsea filter by padj<0.05).
